value.name: Administrators
value.description: Administrators is a built-in group. Its membership is managed by the system. Microsoft Azure subscription administrators fall into this group.

value.name: Developers
value.description: Developers is a built-in group. Its membership is managed by the system. Signed-in users fall into this group.

value.name: Guests
value.description: Guests is a built-in group. Its membership is managed by the system. Unauthenticated users visiting the developer portal fall into this group.
